content: {'id': '0103b164-d785-32c4-a027-093b898711b5', 'contentType': 'STORY', 'title': "India antitrust watchdog clears JSW Paints' bid for up to 75% stake in Akzo Nobel India", 'description': '', 'summary': "India's antitrust body said on Tuesday it has cleared JSW Paints' deal to acquire up to 75% stake in Dutch paint maker Akzo Nobel's Indian unit. The deal, which was announced in June, comes at a time when Indian paint makers are grappling with rising raw material costs and intensifying competition.
